Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.19,0:03:07.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.37,0:03:08.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.38,0:03:10.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续前进 沿途支援友军
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.61,0:03:12.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突破当前宇域
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.56,0:03:14.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乔纳森 不许哭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.09,0:03:17.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想让队长的牺牲白费吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.59,0:03:19.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,击溃维甘阵线！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.07,0:03:21.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.58,0:03:23.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动力下降
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.12,0:03:25.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后备动力呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.43,0:03:27.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早就用上了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.66,0:03:30.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舰长 我知道你很难受
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.84,0:03:31.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但现在是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.92,0:03:34.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除维生系统外 停止其他系统供应
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.00,0:03:36.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全力维持最大航速
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.01,0:03:37.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.96,0:03:41.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机动战士队 迎击侧方来敌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.69,0:03:55.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与敌人陷入混战
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.73,0:03:57.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看准了是敌人再打
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.93,0:03:58.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.97,0:04:11.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这是在干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.59,0:04:17.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰哈特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.31,0:04:21.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,达孜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.71,0:04:23.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰哈特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.34,0:04:25.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你手下的将士们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.62,0:04:28.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与你皆有相同的信念
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.32,0:04:33.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请坚信自己脚下的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.50,0:04:38.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信你创建伊甸的决心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.68,0:04:40.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多勒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.33,0:04:44.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那应该是你发自内心的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.68,0:04:48.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 怎么了 杰哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.61,0:04:49.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德西尔哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.24,0:04:52.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你小子不惜大义灭亲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.63,0:04:57.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难不成 因为这点事就缩了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.46,0:05:01.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.48,0:05:03.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无路可退…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.77,0:05:06.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我留下的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.47,0:05:08.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有通向伊甸之路
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.27,0:05:15.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰哈特大人 有何吩咐？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.12,0:05:21.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芙拉姆 把高达引到迪格玛泽隆炮的射线轴上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.25,0:05:24.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和歌姬号一道 一举歼灭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.56,0:05:27.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连同高达…吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.70,0:05:29.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阻止他们的突进企图
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.63,0:05:31.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扼杀联邦的胜机
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.11,0:05:34.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让这场战斗结束
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.74,0:05:37.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 杰哈特大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.12,0:05:50.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.84,0:05:53.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷伊尔 我去引出高达
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.90,0:05:55.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,指挥拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.44,0:05:56.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.15,0:05:57.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芙拉姆！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.83,0:06:02.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白这个命令意味着什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.82,0:06:05.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,服从这个命令 就意味着…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.77,0:06:11.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少记住那些阵亡者的姓名
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.01,0:06:16.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样善良体贴的杰哈特大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.30,0:06:19.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有想像过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.96,0:06:23.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们即将营造的 伊甸中的风景
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.52,0:06:26.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊甸是 他的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.88,0:06:28.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.31,0:06:31.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我最重要的部下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.95,0:06:34.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这场战斗结束
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.20,0:06:36.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰哈特大人就能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.87,0:06:38.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做回那个体贴善良的杰哈特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.37,0:06:41.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为了保护他…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.50,0:06:43.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保护他善良的心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.38,0:06:51.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,探测系统反应
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.11,0:06:53.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前方路线上出现敌舰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.81,0:06:55.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,右满舵 避让
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.22,0:06:59.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人突然发什么神经？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.09,0:07:10.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狄恩 我会阻止这场战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.40,0:07:11.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.35,0:07:14.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.19,0:07:26.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 进笼子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.58,0:07:27.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死亡之笼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.83,0:07:35.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达 要不是你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.20,0:07:40.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.70,0:07:43.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是用来结束战斗的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.74,0:07:45.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.34,0:07:48.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明什么都不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.07,0:07:57.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上 锥炮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.91,0:08:09.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你坏杰哈特大人的好事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.85,0:08:16.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.08,0:08:26.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.95,0:08:27.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.37,0:08:32.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滚开 臭海盗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.49,0:08:35.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.57,0:08:36.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.90,0:08:50.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芙拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.61,0:08:57.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷伊尔 你不该来这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.23,0:09:00.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早有心理准备
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.53,0:09:06.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上吧 雷伊尔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.48,0:09:08.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了伊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.79,0:09:25.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.56,0:09:28.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么东西来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.58,0:09:30.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,某种恐怖的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.16,0:09:35.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.97,0:09:37.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立即呼叫奥克拉姆德
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.83,0:09:40.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有回答 再次呼叫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.56,0:09:43.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底打得什么算盘 杰哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.03,0:09:47.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们又要使用要塞炮了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.74,0:09:48.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.96,0:09:52.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种武器不是不可能短时间连射吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.58,0:09:54.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敢在战场上进行那种变形
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.83,0:09:56.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其中必有缘由
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.91,0:09:57.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾伦格雷亚斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.17,0:10:00.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人要塞会不会从第二月球获取能量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.81,0:10:03.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为光束炮充能？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.25,0:10:06.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仅从热感器上观察
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.33,0:10:07.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法排除这种可能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.67,0:10:11.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 乱战情况下发射…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.47,0:10:12.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.39,0:10:15.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们打算以自己人为代价
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.27,0:10:17.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带走高达和歌姬号
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.95,0:10:21.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要忘记 对手是维甘！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.75,0:10:23.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么立即下令避让
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.87,0:10:26.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 歌姬号只要继续前进
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.28,0:10:28.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们就会盯住这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.39,0:10:29.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.99,0:10:31.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以歌姬号为饵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.76,0:10:33.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让其他舰艇离开
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.15,0:10:35.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.47,0:10:37.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牺牲自己人？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.67,0:10:39.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰哈特他竟然
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.80,0:10:46.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.02,0:10:49.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从现在起 歌姬号乘员集体离舰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.81,0:10:52.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 离开歌姬号？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.67,0:10:55.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种情况下 出去也会被敌人…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.29,0:10:56.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呆在这里也是被打
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.99,0:10:59.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经要求他们营救撤离的乘员
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.06,0:11:01.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,营救？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.58,0:11:03.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种时候谁来…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.98,0:11:05.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全员 准备撤离
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.18,0:11:09.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请立即前往第三格纳库
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.45,0:11:14.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特·明日野
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.96,0:11:16.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AGE-1 格兰萨 出击
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//----------------------------TXTB-------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.38,0:11:47.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别想跑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.28,0:11:55.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧 芙拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.89,0:12:00.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧 亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.57,0:12:02.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乘员马上就要离舰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.75,0:12:04.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吸引敌人火力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.70,0:12:05.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放弃歌姬号？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.92,0:12:08.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥布莱特 乔纳森
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.90,0:12:11.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉来迟了 明日野司令
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.62,0:12:17.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道就这样跳进宇宙吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.77,0:12:19.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,司令说不要上逃生艇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.50,0:12:21.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们在甲板待命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.41,0:12:24.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舰长 那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.44,0:12:37.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快 到这边来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.32,0:12:39.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我们上海盗船？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.48,0:12:40.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.22,0:12:42.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动作快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.58,0:12:45.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别指望敌人的探测器是瞎子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.73,0:12:51.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全员 登上海盗船巴洛诺克号
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.99,0:12:57.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来还算顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.61,0:13:00.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌姬号
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.76,0:13:05.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老伙计 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.58,0:13:23.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.19,0:13:32.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的战舰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.60,0:13:37.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家抓紧黑猎犬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.92,0:13:38.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用超级推进器
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.03,0:13:41.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一口气离开敌人的射线轴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.50,0:13:44.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.91,0:13:48.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你哪里也别想去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.06,0:13:49.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷伊尔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.99,0:13:51.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.74,0:13:54.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.87,0:13:58.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记住
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.01,0:14:01.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不到最后一刻不许离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.81,0:14:03.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以免敌人察觉我们的作战
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.16,0:14:05.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.19,0:14:06.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了 爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.09,0:14:22.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能 我竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.46,0:14:25.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被这种…被这种…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.25,0:14:29.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷伊尔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.60,0:14:30.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.13,0:14:40.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,队长 看我为你报仇…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.86,0:14:46.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.85,0:14:49.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乔纳森
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.81,0:14:53.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.02,0:14:55.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家抓住黑猎犬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.86,0:14:56.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.79,0:14:57.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.09,0:15:00.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥布莱特先生 请快
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.45,0:15:03.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,决不放过它
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.49,0:15:04.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.13,0:15:14.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个 杂兵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.74,0:15:18.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再垂死挣扎…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.29,0:15:23.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尝尝！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.39,0:15:31.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超级推进器准备
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.29,0:15:33.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,点火倒计时开始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.21,0:15:34.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧 点火同时
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.86,0:15:36.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也用最大功率
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.57,0:15:38.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只当辅助推进
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.71,0:15:39.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.15,0:15:52.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天神…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.92,0:15:54.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥布莱特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.33,0:15:56.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别管我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.80,0:15:59.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们走…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.22,0:16:02.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么 奥布莱特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.76,0:16:05.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们要…活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.91,0:16:10.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾米…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.53,0:16:13.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于能来找你了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.37,0:16:16.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你久等…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.90,0:16:19.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥布莱特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.17,0:16:27.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三台高达全部在射程范围以内
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.20,0:16:29.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.68,0:16:34.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芙拉姆 芙拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.91,0:16:40.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰哈特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.49,0:16:41.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.08,0:16:44.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道道歉也无法得到原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.78,0:16:45.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.95,0:16:48.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰哈特大人 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.29,0:16:50.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会让计划成功
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.88,0:16:51.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.14,0:16:54.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多勒的在天之灵安息
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.78,0:16:56.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别再提哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.04,0:17:00.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能够… 在您手下战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.37,0:17:01.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我最大的光荣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.22,0:17:05.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芙拉姆 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.92,0:17:07.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰哈特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.75,0:17:10.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请让伊甸 回到我们手中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.05,0:17:12.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向你保证
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.67,0:17:16.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定要踏上伊甸！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.18,0:17:21.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰哈特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.92,0:17:24.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发射！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.57,0:17:35.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰哈特 你这该死的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.24,0:18:04.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联邦军战舰 击沉5艘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.28,0:18:05.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.77,0:18:07.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.33,0:18:11.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牺牲了自己最忠诚的部下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.31,0:18:13.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岂有不成之理
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.65,0:18:14.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发现高达！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.67,0:18:17.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.14,0:18:21.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 是高达
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.49,0:18:26.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到底…在干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.54,0:18:31.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底干了些什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.46,0:18:34.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.25,0:18:36.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可悲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.14,0:18:37.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.13,0:18:39.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想胜过我这个哥哥 不是那块料
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.00,0:18:40.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太难看了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.22,0:18:43.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.41,0:18:44.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那块料
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.23,0:18:46.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.01,0:18:48.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论如何也要击落高达
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.91,0:18:52.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赢下这场战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.27,0:18:56.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,司令
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.27,0:18:58.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰哈特大人从法·扎德上出击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.04,0:19:00.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.51,0:19:01.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰哈特大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.17,0:19:15.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.26,0:19:17.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.96,0:19:21.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.93,0:19:23.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.69,0:19:29.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰哈特 不惜牺牲部下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.46,0:19:30.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.12,0:19:34.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要实现夙愿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.26,0:19:35.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为人的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.71,0:19:37.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早已经放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.92,0:19:43.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有人性的大义
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.39,0:19:44.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有何价值可言
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.64,0:19:46.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你懂个屁！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.80,0:19:49.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊甸不是为了让人活得更有人样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.07,0:19:57.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊甸…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.63,0:19:59.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为伊甸献出了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.87,0:20:01.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无怨无悔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.70,0:20:15.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.55,0:20:17.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追上我了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.89,0:20:19.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有你的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.09,0:20:24.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.60,0:20:27.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切…都在逝去…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.94,0:20:31.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么…握不住它…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.38,0:20:33.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总会有把握不住的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.38,0:20:35.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.10,0:20:39.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你多次放走我这个敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.63,0:20:41.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说明作为战士之前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.22,0:20:42.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你首先是一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.32,0:20:45.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想实现…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.76,0:20:49.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊泽尔坎特大人的…夙愿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.99,0:20:51.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的…梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.42,0:20:56.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否则… 我们是为何而活着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.85,0:20:58.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁来告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.27,0:20:59.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.72,0:21:02.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你们度过的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.98,0:21:05.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机动战士社团的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.14,0:21:09.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那段时光是何等的充实
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.41,0:21:14.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定…嫉妒过我的能力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.88,0:21:16.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但其实…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.58,0:21:20.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也在羡慕你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.35,0:21:26.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也…想与爱人生儿育女
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.72,0:21:29.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像你那样…生活…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.60,0:21:30.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.48,0:21:35.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.13,0:21:38.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了 这下可以优胜了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.49,0:21:40.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厉害 太厉害了杰哈特
